{"tid":404651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺兩儀式好撚垃圾","createTime":"2017-09-18T09:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T09:02:16.000Z","uid":94828,"like":304,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99e1b2093d233e98beb5c607298bf92e1f30ec29","tid":404651,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"片又唔係好睇過人<br />\n聲又難撚聽過人<br />\n早排見佢開咗個post<br />\n話咩想屌就屌 放馬過嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/171425_10a92864455aa1eb64b20b2277afbbbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F171425_10a92864455aa1eb64b20b2277afbbbd.jpg&h=bb14bf80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/402924/page/1?ref=ios&amp;action=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/402924/page/1?ref=ios&amp;action=1</a><br />\n點知俾人話多兩句就起哂鋼咁 惡撚過狗<br />\n你以為你乜水呀 網路大紅人呀<br />\n達哥都未必敢咁串嘴啦<br />\n你條垃圾未紅先驕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">縮返入你老母個閪到啦戇鳩仔</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59df961d5b7d6c6d3766753b8d08d2445cd27d0c","tid":404651,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706beefbf3a6b3d3aa5c367c3a7d0f8fe1b25387","tid":404651,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92c17f5584f1a13b08b6cefa1992e5bdbe0c4bbb","tid":404651,"uid":21249,"like":137,"dislike":2,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"聽都未撚聽過"},{"pid":"63e880133f28470682dbdc376a553a6c0adba57e","tid":404651,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"人哋好撚勁㗎"},{"pid":"61d2f6c08fe343366a800f22753d3012d62f83c7","tid":404651,"uid":55614,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"ci