而只係著重view數"},{"pid":"9fbd62399f76edc28f4681faca4f74326e5e94e1","tid":404651,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:05:57.000Z","msg":"初初都ok，而家變哂質，不了"},{"pid":"0bb3e31fceb6163701ad26592f6c844d20fef15c","tid":404651,"uid":7916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:39:08.000Z","msg":"把聲好撚毒"},{"pid":"c1d09ad0625abf4fecb89a8bc5f8a5a24af237c0","tid":404651,"uid":1748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>把聲好撚毒</blockquote><br />\n睇名都知毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067b21af70904e87247ca343f312fd3b6f4c3ddf","tid":404651,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢最初係高登叫人睇佢DS gameplay果陣 當時佢個名仲係叫亂世J人 我果陣仲會俾下意見 提議下佢有咩可以改善 當然佢都好有禮貌咁回應 果時我覺得呢個巴打拍片繼續落去都應該幾好睇 但去到佢拍仁王開始 我已經覺得開始有d變質 語氣同態度都開始囂 唔知係開始多人睇定係巴打覺得同朋友講野係呢種語氣 感覺已經係為拍而拍 以前少人睇既時候 你反而最有心機做 但依家反而只係著重view數</blockquote><br />\n通常啲人好撚紅先開始變質   佢果隻就係以為自己好撚紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3365af054c668bd6294ae5b74fe532e8e0490db","tid":404651,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得兩儀式個channel好撚高質<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170606/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/170606/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post都大把人話佢學達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   唔知點解果時有人幫佢護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d80656ed959186f1b8769abbedeab6d03f8b90c","tid":404651,"uid":1748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人覺得兩儀式個channel好撚高質<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170606/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">ht